data.description: Walk right in to this 4-bedroom, 3-bath bi-level home for sale in Hamburg, NJ. The house features vinyl wood floors throughout, a large deck that extends the full length of the home, and a master bedroom with a sliding glass door to the deck. The  kitchen comes equipped with a stove, dishwasher, and refrigerator. The property has public water and sewer services and a newly paved driveway. It's conveniently located just 2 minutes from Crystal Springs Golf Resort, which has 6 golf courses on-site. Perfect for entertaining and comfortable living with extra large entertainment room on the lower level. with 4 seasons of fun in the backyard you will never get bored.
